      <title>《明报》称中国将提高赴港旅客免税限额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/china-said-to-raise-duty-free-shopping-limit-for-visitors-to-hk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据周四的一份报纸报道，内地游客很快将获准在香港享受更多免税购物，北京方面将把购物限额提高至多六倍，以提振香港低迷的零售业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/china-said-to-raise-duty-free-shopping-limit-for-visitors-to-hk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
