      <title>印度金融家的债务以 2020 年以来最大的利差吸引买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/indian-financiers-debt-lures-buyers-on-widest-spread-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度影子银行正在吸引该国一些最大的基金经理，因为它们的债券相对于主权债券的溢价达到了近四年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/indian-financiers-debt-lures-buyers-on-widest-spread-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
